{"tid":1387300,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"3/8，4/8 集會遊行取消，改室內搞！！！","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T14:04:56.000Z","uid":275971,"like":7,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee413ac9afbdfbdbd67082459894104e877173ab","tid":1387300,"uid":275971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:36:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">其實有漫人唸過改下集會遊行既方式，全部轉戰室內外，有冷氣有廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">我提議3/8 去18區商場Window shopping, 塞爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">4/8 大家一齊去送機，塞爆機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實我開始5係好明點解遊行集會一定要室外搞，室外好多狗，室內就5比帶狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然係咪都沒不反對通知書，點解仲要係室外搞呢？又熱又多狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">室內搞仲可以搞佢經濟</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有搞經濟呢場運動先會成功呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n真心遊行過去2個月已經遊夠，最多搞埋未搞既區，其實民意已經企係我地個邊，大家都開始盲目，要有d 新意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近期大家話罷工，都係想搞經濟姐，但罷工難成事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋我想講，我真係5想再見到有人被補受傷，如果勇武想留守，想衝，和理都應該留守，人多就5洗怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家加油！"},{"pid":"6e8982d3c6dd3d9a204e74476f4f3bac744763f3","tid":1387300,"uid":275971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ee413ac9afbdfbdbd67082459894104e877173ab","tid":1387300,"uid":275971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit